membership:
The ABBL is a member of the European Banking Federation (EBF) since 1960, where it is represented in the executive bodies, as well as in the major technical committees and working groups, and contributes to on-going works of the federation.&#xd;
The ABBL is a member of UEL (Union des Entreprises Luxembourgeoises).&#xd;
The ABBL is a member of the European Covered Bonds Council.&#xd;
The ABBL is a member of ECRI (CEPS). http://www.ecri.eu/new/index.php
